{"tid":2501320,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"揸A仔同1系邊個賤啲？","createTime":"2021-04-23T09:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T13:49:48.000Z","uid":330057,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31ccdfff2c1b6728ef695c6d6db62b5fe9ae1225","tid":2501320,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"1系，多數都係保險/地產狗想買車但係又買唔起啲貴嘢，唯有揸住架三缸垃圾都算係叫揸寶馬<br />\n臭四當名車咁揸，好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA仔，又係啲保險/地產MK狗專用臭四座駕<br />\n明明A200係都要貼個AM雞章，狗屎垃圾又要改到條喉嘈過林寶，而且10個A仔，九個鍾意亂cut線，左穿右插。好心你哋啦揸緊架臭四咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以1系同A仔究竟邊個賤啲？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gB6p2M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgB6p2M4.jpg&h=26159f14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0o9SsdL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0o9SsdL.jpg&h=ddf47126&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15725772228f1b5f0f31e51f3d9d81a8141a482b","tid":2501320,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"二年以上嘅一系我直頭係唔會上車<br />\n三缸成日燈位震到我急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72399bef7295b341b2baa219bb3a21b9a9c86307","tid":2501320,"uid":392206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"誠哥同四叔唔好鬥邊嗰賤啲啦<br />\n平手好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3ab1ec7c8a1ed2db5f0de8debb47358b594907","tid":2501320,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"咁快有傻閪負評<br />\n有咁多時間去賺多啲錢上少啲連登<br />\n買㗎好啲嘅車，對十二指腸都好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ae7fde23e3d9cae1644dbde66b72f919d21c43","tid":2501320,"uid":374479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"想知po主揸緊咩"},{"pid